  "prompt": "Where can I found a large range of formal and evening wear in Gold Coast?",
  "response": "In the Gold Coast, there are several places where you can find a wide range of formal and evening wear:\n\n1. **Pacific Fair Shopping Centre**: Located in Broadbeach, Pacific Fair is one of the largest shopping centers in the Gold Coast and offers a variety of stores that sell formal and evening wear, including high-end boutiques and department stores.\n\n2. **Robina Town Centre**: This shopping centre in Robina has numerous fashion retailers, including specialized stores for formal and evening attire.\n\n3. **Harbour Town Outlet Shopping Centre**: Situated in Biggera Waters, Harbour Town offers discounted prices on many brand-name stores, which can include formal and evening wear.\n\n4. **Designer Boutiques**: The Gold Coast has several designer boutiques that offer unique and high-end formal wear. Some areas to check out include the beachfront precincts in Surfers Paradise and Broadbeach.\n\n5. **David Jones and Myer**: Both of these department stores, located within major shopping centres like Pacific Fair and Robina Town Centre, carry a good selection of formal and evening wear.\n\n6. **Local Bridal and Formal Wear Stores**: There are specialized stores scattered throughout the Gold Coast that focus solely on bridal and formal wear, such as Ferrari Formalwear & Bridal, and others.\n\n7. **Online Options**: Many local boutiques and retailers also offer online shopping, which can be a convenient way to browse their collections and find the perfect outfit.\n\nIt is always a good idea to check store websites or call ahead to confirm their inventory and any specific requirements you might have.",
